Pastime - Spend time doing what you love - (c) 2012

Project Structure
-----------------
the pastime user web application
src - all source code
	main/java - backend java source code
	main/webapp - frontend html/css/javascript code
	
To build a deployable web app archive (.war):
---------------------------------------------
./gradlew build
See build/libs/pastime.war

To run the web app:
-------------------
./gradlew jettyRun

Point your preferred web browser at http://localhost:8080